    "description": "HEXAD is a single and multiplayer competitive turn-based tactical RPG with ARPG-like itemization and crafting and a shared town hub where you manage your team of Heroes. Play in multiple game modes against AI or other players!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Multiple game modes</strong>, including Story, Adventure, Multiplayer PvP, and the Crucible.<br></li><li> <strong>Classic tactical combat</strong> on a hex grid where elevation and positioning matter.<br></li><li> Equip your Heroes with <strong>56 unique items and skills</strong> ranging from common rarity to artifacts.<br></li><li> <strong>Earn experience </strong> and level your Heroes to further increase base stats.<br></li><li> <strong>Customize Hero appearance</strong> by changing facial features and equipment colors.<br></li><li> <strong>Collect dozens of Cosmetic Items</strong> to show off your unique style.<br></li><li> <strong>Idiosyncratic Item Crafting</strong> allows changing and upgrading components to create unorthodox hybrid builds.<br></li><li> Rise to the top of the <strong>Leaderboards</strong> in PvP, Crafting, Adventuring, Mercantile, or the Crucible. </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>HEXAD gameplay follows the classic turn based tactics model with a few twists.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The <strong>turn timer</strong> keeps multiplayer games moving and adds a challenge to game modes.<br></li><li> <strong>Status effects</strong> can stack on tiles and Heroes. Certain skills will consume multiple stacks for devastating effects.<br></li><li> <strong>Player vs Player focused</strong> with game modes that normalize item stats to put players on a level playing field. Geared PvP game modes let you show off your crafted items and your builds true power.</li></ul>",
